<Link id="l00218" /><CodeLine lineNumber="218"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// registers. Such parameters can be sign- or zero-extended at the</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00223" /><CodeLine lineNumber="223"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// defining those virtual registers, and in practice those are COPY</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00224" /><CodeLine lineNumber="224"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// instructions from a physical to a virtual register. In such cases,</span></CodeLine>
